  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055710/extras/16ff66dc36aecec5edddc98386cf12e8.avif?t=1739267497\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055710/extras_big/16ff66dc36aecec5edddc98386cf12e8.avif?t=1739267497 width=800 height=600 /></span>Dig into arcade action with a twist in <strong>Rumble Crumble</strong>. <strong>Rumble</strong>, the star-nosed mole, has lost his way: it's your job to help him reach his friends on the surface! <strong>Collect gems</strong> to earn points, <strong>gobble grubs</strong> to top-up energy reserves and grab <strong>power-ups</strong> to transform Rumble’s digging abilities. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Procedural Level Design</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055710/extras/9d35ca9ae00d90544af0bbbeededbd1d.avif?t=1739267497\" width=600 height=92 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each run is <strong>procedurally generated</strong>, meaning you’ll never dig the same stage twice! Variety is the spice of life…</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>3 depths & 4 difficulty modes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055710/extras/bbf225887595f78e56aab6070b0599b8.avif?t=1739267497\" width=600 height=92 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover new environments, power-ups & obstacles as you progress through stages. From a casual <strong>EASY 50m</strong> run to a tricky <strong>EXTREME ENDLESS</strong>, Rumble Crumble caters to all ages and player abilities. No digging experience required!  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>20+ items and power-ups to unlock</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055710/extras/93e3a99e62b67772dcc08ed15533c710.avif?t=1739267497\" width=600 height=92 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over <strong>20 different items and power-ups</strong> to enhance your digging and amplify the gameplay. From the <strong>Rhino Beetle</strong> for crushing blocks with ease, to the <strong>Ginger Root</strong> for setting the underground alight; who knows what you’ll discover? </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Stack power-ups for unique effects</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055710/extras/89bc3a8575acd8ee5d75c995caab52a9.avif?t=1739267497\" width=600 height=92 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Combining power-ups</strong> can wield incredible results! The possibilities are endless… </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>100+ achievements</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055710/extras/6aece7e1432a398798f0b6ce263accba.avif?t=1739267497\" width=600 height=92 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From time-trials & high scores to bug-eating and dry-runs, there’s plenty to keep you busy and get you re-thinking how you dig.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Test your stamina & discover secrets in ENDLESS mode</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055710/extras/56ce87f5f3d20d0cf8ad753357c318e3.avif?t=1739267497\" width=600 height=92 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock <strong>ENDLESS</strong> mode & push your digging abilities to the limit. How far can you dig?</p>",
